sp.p:
To end the Matter then, Neighbours, I declare I'm for a Common-Wealth;
let us therefore, nemini conumdiscendre, plot against these Gods aforesaid,
and their Government: We'll have no longer Arbitrary-Power: We'll
bring 'em down to the Station of Constables; Then any one of us, Neighbours,
may hope to come into Office in his Turn.

